The '''Blade series''' was a series of rugged but somewhat primitive [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheric]] fighters and [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] produced by, among others, [[Tarrvin-on-Kallik]] on [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. Blade series fighters were distinguished by mounting both forward- and aft-firing [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]]. Most were designed for atmospheric combat, but could be modified relatively easily for [[Realspace/Legends|space]] use. Some models even featured [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrives]].

All Blade models about which significant details are known had split tails.

